quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  113,1,"SAY: I betake me for refuge to the Lord of the DAY BREAK"
  113,2,Against the mischiefs of his creation
  113,3,And against the mischief of the night when it overtaketh me
  113,4,And against the mischief of weird women
  113,5,And against the mischief of the envier when he envieth